title: Top 30 Country March 11, 2014
description:
Hey folks, considering there were no new singles on the March 4 chart I decided it would be pointless to post a new upload last week.  This week, however, we have 2 new songs and a better shuffle of solid Hot Country hits.  Here are the Top 30 U.S. Country Hits as ranked by Mediabase for the week of March 11, 2014.  Enjoy the music!

01 Lady Antebellum - Compass (2:58)
02 Jason Aldean - When She Says Baby (2:48)
03 Dierks Bentley - I Hold On (4:32)
04 Frankie Ballard - Helluva Life (3:48)
05 Blake Shelton - Doin' What She Likes (3:38)

07 Randy Houser - Goodnight Kiss (3:23)
08 Scotty McCreery - See You Tonight (3:41)
09 Jerrod Niemann - Drink To That All Night (3:39)
10 Eric Church - Give Me Back My Hometown (4:03)
11 Rascal Flatts - Rewind (3:17)
12 Dan + Shay - 19 You + Me (3:33)
13 Cole Swindell - Chillin' It (3:13)
14 Brett Eldredge - Beat Of The Music (2:55)
15 Brantley Gilbert - Bottoms Up (3:34)
16 Thomas Rhett - Get Me Some Of That (3:03)
17 Keith Urban - Cop Car (4:08)
18 Brad Paisley - The Mona Lisa (3:40)
19 Justin Moore - Lettin' The Night Roll (3:18)
20 Miranda Lambert - Automatic (4:03)
21 Florida Georgia Line & Luke Bryan - This Is How We Roll (3:39)
22 Craig Morgan - Wake Up Lovin' You (3:16)
23 Kip Moore - Young Love (3:46)

RECURRENT Danielle Bradbery - The Heart of Dixie (3:26)
RECURRENT Luke Bryan - Drink A Beer (3:18)

Have a great week from the Baz-Master
